com.tedros.fxapi.animation

Class ExponentialInterpolator

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.animation.Interpolator
      • com.tedros.fxapi.animation.EasingInterpolator
        • com.tedros.fxapi.animation.ExponentialInterpolator

  • public class ExponentialInterpolator
extends EasingInterpolator
    An exponential interpolator.

    This interpolator accelerates very fast and decelerates very late.

    The following curve illustrates the interpolation.

    The math in this class is taken from http://www.robertpenner.com/easing/.

    Author:
    Christian Schudt
